<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦١٥٤ -<span class="c5"> حدَّثنا عُبَيْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ مُوسَى:</span> أخبَرَنا حَنْظَلَةُ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ سَالِمٍ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَنِ ابْنِ عُمَرَ <span class="special">﵄</span>، عَنِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لأَنْ يَمْتَلِئَ جَوْفُ أَحَدِكُمْ قَيْحًا خَيْرٌ لَهُ مِنْ أَنْ يَمْتَلِئَ شِعْرًا»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>